videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets the ball in the high post and squares up to hit the jump shot.
videos.headline: Ayton gets going with jumper

videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets the entry pass and goes up for a powerful slam in traffic.
videos.headline: Ayton playing physical in post

videos.description: Collin Sexton drives and hits a difficult floater over the Arizona defense for his first points.
videos.headline: Sexton hits floater over sea of arms

videos.description: Deandre Ayton aggressively attacks the boards and elevates to finish the crafty putback.
videos.headline: Ayton crashes glass and gets putback dunk

videos.description: Allonzo Trier pushes the tempo and zips a pass to Deandre Ayton who slams it with two hands.
videos.headline: Sweet pass sets up Ayton slam

videos.description: Donta Hall is 6-6 with 14 points after taking it himself for the layup.
videos.headline: Hall goes coast-to-coast on steal and score

videos.description: Alabama's Collin Sexton pulls up from way downtown to put Alabama up 6 in the second half.
videos.headline: Sexton pulls up from NBA range

videos.description: Collin Sexton races down the court and avoids the charge with a ferocious Eurostep move as Alabama trails by 76-74.
videos.headline: Sexton shows elite speed on Eurostep finish

videos.description: Deandre Ayton takes the game into his own hands and sinks two jumpers late in the second half to give him a career-high 29 points.
videos.headline: Arizona pulls away on back-to-back Ayton jumpers

videos.description: Arizona's Deandre Ayton scored a career-high 29 points and grabbed 18 boards in Arizona's 88-82 win over Alabama.
videos.headline: All of Ayton's skills on display in win over Alabama

videos.description: Freshman Collin Sexton scores 30 points against the Wildcats but the Tide drop to 7-3.
videos.headline: Sexton shines in Bama's close loss vs. Arizona 88-82
